60,000 THANK YOU's 🥳 Thank you for being the absolute sweetest, kindest, most supportive little corner of Instagram. 🤍

Thank you to @uglyducklingnails
for the opportunities you've blessed me with, for giving me the honor of being an Educator for your brand, and for creating the BEST products that make creating my teeny-tiny little artwork that much more enjoyable.

I appreciate everyone who follows, everyone one who likes, comments, saves and sends messages.  I try my best to (eventually) respond to comments and messages, but please know, I read each one with a warm heart. And I still get just as excited when I see a new message or comment pop up. Thanks for so much support over the years - I don't say it enough, but you guys are the best!

Big, warm, squishy hugs & lots of love,
N xo
